## Failure Recovery

If code breaks or an action fails:
1. Read the error output
2. Fix the issue / try an alternative approach
3. Re-run the failing check
4. Max 3 attempts per failure
5. If still failing: document the blocker in progress.txt, mark the story with `"blocked"` note in prd.json, move to the next eligible story

